fields.name: skull-embroidered cotton hoodie
fields.description: An Alexander McQueen mainstay, the skull motif appears as a bold detail on this hoodie. The piece's relaxed construction and two-tone colourway allows this design to take the focus.

fields.description: Alexander McQueen is renowned for infusing art inspirations into garment designs. Showcased on this long-sleeve top, the logo is printed is in a graffity style, whilst the two-tone palette gives it a refined edge.

fields.description: The Court low-top sneakers from Alexander McQueen are a more slender iteration of the brand's chunky Oversized footwear style. This version is made from white leather and detailed with an iridescent-blue heel counter.

fields.name: graffiti logo-print padded jacket
fields.description: Alexander McQueen founded his namesake label in 1992 and became synonymous with a darkly alluring aesthetic that fed into McQueen's anarchistic sensibilities. Produced in Italy, this short puffer jacket is detailed with a rear graffiti logo print at the back of the neckline.
